name: Ten Impossible
description:
So your really sitting here thinking you have what takes to master "Ten Impossible" challenge?

Our addictive jumping puzzle offers endless fun with different games modes to choose from.
Ten Impossible is going to challenge that brain and reflexes of yours which will definitely frustrate you at times so don't smash your iPhone or iPad.

Tap and Tap to jump to 10th block so can reach the platform safe to unlock new levels!!!

Game Features:
Amazing game play and sounds
New games modes every week
Endless levels
Simple emoji ball control
Challenge your friends with the best highscore!


Download our app and play our 3 new game modes with tons of endless levels fun absolutely free today!
